CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774440171
OL,3,CUS issues 15-point ceasefire plan but
OL,4,CIran still insists they are not in
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FThe US has submitted a 15-point
OL,8,Fceasefire deal to Iranian officials in
OL,9,Fa bid to end the ongoing war in the
OL,10,FMiddle East, as Iran's military mocked
OL,11,Fattempts at an agreement being made.
OL,13,FThe Trump administration's plan was
OL,14,Fsubmitted to Iran by intermediaries
OL,15,Ffrom Pakistan, who have offered to
OL,16,Fhost renewed negotiations between
OL,17,FWashington and Tehran, an official
OL,18,Ftold AP on Tuesday.
OL,20,FThe exact details of the plan have not
OL,21,Fbeen published.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774440171
OL,3,CUS issues 15-point ceasefire plan but
OL,4,CIran still insists they are not in
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FHowever, Israeli media reported that
OL,8,FIran dismantling its nuclear
OL,9,Fcapabilities, committing to not
OL,10,Fpursuing nuclear weapons and no longer
OL,11,Fenriching nuclear material were among
OL,12,Fthe points.
OL,14,FUS President Donald Trump claimed Iran
OL,15,Fhad agreed to "never have a nuclear
OL,16,Fweapon" while speaking to reporters in
OL,17,Fthe White house on Tuesday, stating
OL,18,Fthat the countries are "in
OL,19,Fnegotiations right now".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774440171
OL,3,CUS issues 15-point ceasefire plan but
OL,4,CIran still insists they are not in
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FBut the speaker of Iran's parliament,
OL,13,FMohammad Bagher Qalibaf, has denied
OL,14,Fany direct talks are taking place,
OL,15,Fwhile an Iranian military spokesman
OL,16,Fmocked the attempt at a deal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774440171
OL,3,CUS issues 15-point ceasefire plan but
OL,4,CIran still insists they are not in
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,F"Have your internal conflicts reached
OL,8,Fthe point where you are negotiating
OL,9,Fwith yourselves?" said Lt. Col.
OL,10,FEbrahim Zolfaghari, a spokesman for
OL,11,Fthe headquarters, said in a
OL,12,Fprerecorded video aired on state
OL,13,Ftelevision on Wednesday.
OL,15,F"The one claiming to be a global
OL,16,Fsuperpower would have already gotten
OL,17,Fout of this mess if it could.
OL,19,F"Don't dress up your defeat as an
OL,20,Fagreement. Your era of empty promises
OL,21,Fhas come to an end."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774440171
OL,3,CUS issues 15-point ceasefire plan but
OL,4,CIran still insists they are not in
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FZolfaghari went on to say the fighting
OL,8,Fwould continue, stating that stability
OL,9,Fin the region was only guaranteed by
OL,10,F"the strong hand of our armed forces".
OL,12,F"Our first and last word has been the
OL,13,Fsame from day one, and it will stay
OL,14,Fthat way: Someone like us will never
OL,15,Fcome to terms with someone like you.
OL,16,FNot now, not ever," Zolfaghari said of
OL,17,Fthe US.
OL,19,FUS sending more troops to Middle East
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774440171
OL,3,CUS issues 15-point ceasefire plan but
OL,4,CIran still insists they are not in
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FIt comes as the Pentagon is preparing
OL,8,Fto deploy two Marine units that will
OL,9,Fadd around 5,000 Marines and thousands
OL,10,Fof sailors to the region in the coming
OL,11,Fdays, a person with knowledge of the
OL,12,Fmove who spoke on condition of
OL,13,Fanonymity told AP.
OL,15,FTrump is making the manoeuvre - which
OL,16,Fwill supplement some 50,000 troops
OL,17,Falready in the region - to give
OL,18,Fhimself "max flexibility" on what to
OL,19,Fdo next, they said.
OL,26,@zD@IOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
