OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774440171
OL,3,CUS issues 15-point ceasefire plan but
OL,4,CIran still insists they are not in
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FThe source also said Israeli
OL,8,Fofficials, who have been advocating
OL,9,Ffor Trump to continue the war against
OL,10,FIran, were surprised by the US
OL,11,Fceasefire plan.
OL,13,FTrump had previously given Iran a 48-
OL,14,Fhour deadline to open the Strait of
OL,15,FHormuz - a vital oil shipping waterway
OL,16,F- before he targeted the nation's
OL,17,Fpower plants, which he extended by
OL,18,Ffive days on Monday.
OL,20,FThai oil tanker passes through Strait
OL,21,Fof Hormuz
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
