OL,3,CUS issues 15-point ceasefire plan but
OL,4,CIran still insists they are not in
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FA Thai oil tanker has transited
OL,8,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz safely
OL,9,Fafter Iran told the UN Security
OL,10,FCouncil "non-hostile" ships would be
OL,11,Fallowed to pass.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
