OL,3,CUS issues 15-point ceasefire plan but
OL,4,CIran still insists they are not in
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FPosting on X on Tuesday evening,
OL,8,FIran's foreign ministry said "non-
OL,9,Fhostile vessels, including those
OL,10,Fbelonging to or associated with other
OL,11,Fstates" could use the waterway,
OL,12,F"provided that they neither
OL,13,Fparticipate in nor support acts of
OL,14,Faggression against Iran and fully
OL,15,Fcomply with the declared safety and
OL,16,Fsecurity regulations".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
