OL,3,CUS issues 15-point ceasefire plan but
OL,4,CIran still insists they are not in
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FEnergy company Bangchak Corporation
OL,8,Fconfirmed a crude oil tanker - which
OL,9,Fhad been anchored in the Persian Gulf
OL,10,Fsince March 11 - had made it through
OL,11,Fthe passageway and was now on its way
OL,12,Fto Thailand.
OL,14,FIn a statement published Tuesday, it
OL,15,Fthanked the Thai government for
OL,16,Fcoordinating with authorities in Iran
OL,17,Fand Oman.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
