OL,3,CUS issues 15-point ceasefire plan but
OL,4,CIran still insists they are not in
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,F"The tanker is currently on its way
OL,8,Facross the Indian Ocean and is
OL,9,Fexpected to deliver crude oil to
OL,10,FThailand in early April," the company
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"Bangchak continues to monitor the
OL,14,Fsituation closely and hopes the
OL,15,Fremainder of the journey will proceed
OL,16,Fsmoothly, while prioritising safe
OL,17,Ftransportation and steady energy
OL,18,Fsupply for the country."
OL,20,FIsrael launches attack on Iran, as
OL,21,FGulf nations struck overnight
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
