OL,3,CUS issues 15-point ceasefire plan but
OL,4,CIran still insists they are not in
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FEarly on Wednesday, the Israeli
OL,8,Fmilitary announced it had begun new
OL,9,Fwide-scale attacks on Iran, targeting
OL,10,Fgovernment infrastructure, with
OL,11,Fwitnesses reporting airstrikes in the
OL,12,Fnorthwestern city of Qazvin.
OL,14,FMissile alert sirens also began early
OL,15,Fin the morning in Israel and Bahrain
OL,16,Fas Iran launched its own attacks,
OL,17,Fwhile Saudi Arabia said it had
OL,18,Fdestroyed at least eight drones in its
OL,19,FEastern Province.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
