CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774440171
OL,3,CUS issues 15-point ceasefire plan but
OL,4,CIran still insists they are not in
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FKuwait said it shot down multiple
OL,8,Fdrones overnight, but one hit a fuel
OL,9,Ftank at Kuwait International Airport,
OL,10,Fsparking a fire.
OL,12,FIsraeli military warned people in
OL,13,Fseven southern suburbs of Beirut,
OL,14,FLebanon, to evacuate on Tuesday night,
OL,15,Fas it continued to strike what it
OL,16,Fdescribes as "Hezbollah
OL,17,Finfrastructure" in the area.
OL,19,FOil prices fluctuate as US and Iran
OL,20,Fdisagree on ceasefire claims
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
