PN,30514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774440171
OL,3,CUS issues 15-point ceasefire plan but
OL,4,CIran still insists they are not in
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FBrent crude oil - the benchmark for
OL,8,Foil prices - dropped nearly 6% during
OL,9,Fthe early hours of Wednesday morning
OL,10,Fas Trump spoke of plans for a
OL,11,Fceasefire with Iran, bringing it under
OL,12,F$100 (#74.74) a barrel.
OL,14,FPrices then began fluctuating again
OL,15,Fafter Iran's military spokesperson
OL,16,Fdismissed Trump's claims of
OL,17,Fnegotiation.
OL,19,FBefore the US-Israeli war with Iran,
OL,20,Foil prices had not been above $100 a
OL,21,Fbarrel for four years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
